  "description": "<p>索尼PS4游戏机的手柄DualShock 4灯光条在设计上算挺漂亮，而且具有不错的功能性，不过这个灯光条是不能关闭的，也就是说只要手柄还开着，灯光条也就随之保持开启状态。<strong>索尼全球工作室 （Worldwide Studio）董事长吉田修平（Shuhei Yoshida）在回答提问时也确认了此灯光条不可关闭用于省电。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e5eda40/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243907.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9APS4%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E7%81%AF%E5%85%89%E6%9D%A1%E5%B0%86%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%8D%95%E7%8B%AC%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243907.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9APS4%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E7%81%AF%E5%85%89%E6%9D%A1%E5%B0%86%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%8D%95%E7%8B%AC%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243907.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9APS4%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E7%81%AF%E5%85%89%E6%9D%A1%E5%B0%86%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%8D%95%E7%8B%AC%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243907.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9APS4%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E7%81%AF%E5%85%89%E6%9D%A1%E5%B0%86%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%8D%95%E7%8B%AC%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243907.ht